Ibarra Real Nova Bold (IbarraRealNova-Bold.ttf)

STAT

static font

Variable font must have a STAT table.

No check of STAT table for static fonts included, yet. Static fonts do not need to have a STAT table. It is only recommended by Microsoft, not required.
More infos here:
https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/typography/opentype/spec/stat

Ibarra Real Nova Italic (IbarraRealNova-Italic.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'IbarraRealNova-Italic', Everything looks good.

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'IbarraRealNova-Italic', Everything looks good.

MS NID 6

Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'IbarraRealNova-SemiBold', Everything looks good.

Ibarra Real Nova SemiBold Regular (IbarraRealNova-SemiBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Ibarra Real Nova' + 'Space' + NID 17 'SemiBold' = NID 1 'Ibarra Real Nova SemiBold'.

Ibarra Real Nova SemiBold Italic (IbarraRealNova-SemiBoldItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Ibarra Real Nova' + 'Space' + NID 17 'SemiBold Italic' = NID 1 'Ibarra Real Nova SemiBold' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Ibarra Real Nova Bold (IbarraRealNova-Bold.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'IbarraRealNova-Bold', Everything looks good.

Pass

Ibarra Real Nova Bold (IbarraRealNova-Bold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'IbarraRealNova-Bold', Everything looks good.

Pass
